<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title><%= content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title) : "Tmp" %></title>
		<%= csrf_meta_tags %>

		<!-- Le HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML elements -->
		<!--[if lt IE 9]>
		  <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
		<![endif]-->

		<%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", :media => "all" %>

		<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Merriweather:400,300,700,900' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
		<link href="images/favicon.ico" rel="shortcut icon">
		<link href="images/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon">
		<link href="images/apple-touch-icon-72x72.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="72x72">
		<link href="images/apple-touch-icon-114x114.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="114x114">
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			
			<%= link_to image_tag('fork_me.png'), 'https://github.com/jgrevich/fugacious', :style => 'position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;', :title => "Fork me on GitHub"  %>
			
			<header id='header'>
				<div id="fugus">
					<%= link_to image_tag('fugur.svg', :id => :fugur ), root_url %>
					<%= link_to image_tag('fugu.svg', :id => :fugu ), root_url %>					
				</div>
				<%= link_to image_tag('logo.svg'), root_url %>
				<h2><%= link_to raw('open source short &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; term secure messaging'), root_url %></h2>
			</header>

			<div class="content">
				<%= yield %>
			</div><!--/content-->

		</div> <!-- /container -->


		<section id='info_panel'>
			<div class='container'>
				<nav>
					<ul>
						<%= content_tag :li, link_to( "About", "", :class => :selected ) %>
						<%= content_tag :li, link_to( "Privacy Policy", privacy_path ) %>
						<%= content_tag :li, link_to( "Github", "https://github.com/jgrevich/fugacious" ) %>
					</ul>
				</nav>
										
				<p>Fugacio.us is a tool designed to assist in sending sensitive information through email or other insecure messaging protocols.</p>
				<p>One can send a username through email, save the password with us, and feel comfortable sharing user credentials without sacrificing security or usability.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		

		<footer>
			<h2>fu ga cious: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; adj&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\fyü-´a-shes\&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :fleeting &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :ephemeral</h2>
		</footer>
			

		<!-- Javascripts
		================================================== -->
		<!-- Placed at the end of the document so the pages load faster -->
		<%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
	</body>
</html>
